ipv6 at slac ipv6 at slac the current addressing schema for the ipv6 network at slac is described in the document ipv6 address allocation at slac the current setup of the slac ipv6 network is comprised of 2 nodes nereus and epaphus these nodes are on our test ipv6 network more detailed description of the setup procedure can be viewed in slac ipv6 installation notes we are using the ipv6 network for pinger monitoring since july 2003 results collected so far can be viewed from an ipv6 machine ipv6 pinger results ipv6 server to have instructions on how to install the ipv6 stack on your machine refer to the following link comments to ipv6 l ipv6 slac mailing list last modified fri may 21 13 51 49 pdt 2004
